        "content": "<p>I just merged a really big PR that redoes the login and registration pages fairly extensively.  Deployed it on <a href=\"http://chat.zulip.org\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://chat.zulip.org\">chat.zulip.org</a> a few minutes ago.  Everyone should check the new version out and let us know what you think!  Also, there's almost certainly some bugs; we should find them all :)</p>",
        "id": 193465,
        "sender_full_name": "Tim Abbott",
        "timestamp": 1493255192
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>So far, the things I've noticed:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The secondary pages in the password reset flow are wrong</li>\n<li>There isn't enough space to give a longer name like \"Zulip development community\"</li>\n<li>The current limits on the length of the description text in organization admin UI are much shorter than what makes sense visually with this design.</li>\n<li>The black default background looks a bit funny with the transparent realm icon we're using.</li>\n</ul>",
        "id": 193466,
        "sender_full_name": "Tim Abbott",
        "timestamp": 1493255266
    },
